y''\n|Thistledown Press\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:#B0C4DE\" |{{sort|20091|[[2008 in literature|2009]]}}\n|{{sortname|Pasha|Malla}}\n|''The Withdrawal Method''\n|[[House of Anansi Press]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen;\" |{{sort|20092|[[2008 in literature|2009]]}}\n|{{sortname|Ian|Colford|nolink=1}}\n|''Halifax for Evidence''\n|[[The Porcupine's Quill]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen\" |{{sort|20093|[[2008 in literature|2009]]}}\n|{{sortname|Rebecca|Rosenblum}}\n|''Once''\n|Biblioasis\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20094|[[2008 in literature|2009]]}}\n|{{sortname|Ahmad|Saidullah|nolink=1}}\n|''Happiness and other Disorders''\n|[[Key Porter Books]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20095|[[2008 in literature|2009]]}}\n|{{sortname|Betsy|Trumpener|nolink=1}}\n|''The Butcher of Penetang''\n|Caitlin Press\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:#B0C4DE\" |{{sort|20101|[[2009 in literature|2010]]}}\n|{{sortname|Sarah|Roberts|nolink=1}}\n|''Wax Boats''\n|Caitlin Press\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen;\" |{{sort|20102|[[2009 in literature|2010]]}}\n|{{sortname|Deborah|Willis|Deborah Willis (Canadian author)}}\n|''Vanishing and Other St